12 Dec 2025 08:29:23 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://wenchiehlee.github.io/mkdocs-life/feed_rss_updated.xml">Wen-Chieh Lee的生活</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://wenchiehlee.github.io/mkdocs-life/blog/2025/12/%E5%BF%AB%E6%A8%82%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9%E6%84%9F%E9%80%A3%E7%B5%90%E6%84%9F%E8%88%87%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E6%84%9F/</guid> </item> <item> <title>貪嗔痴的底層邏輯：我對事、我對人、我對我</title> <description>&lt;p&gt;三毒常被說得玄，但拆開就是三個很日常的執著：我怎麼看「事」、我怎麼對「人」、我怎麼理解「我」。把框架理清，三毒的運作就一目了然，也能對照前兩篇的「我對事／我對人／我對我」架構。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;!!! abstract &#34;速覽&#34; - 貪（我對事）：把慾望變成「必須」，快樂被外部事件綁架，期待—要求—焦慮的迴圈越轉越快。...&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://wenchiehlee.github.io/mkdocs-life/blog/2025/12/%E8%B2%AA%E5%97%94%E7%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%BA%95%E5%B1%A4%E9%82%8F%E8%BC%AF%E6%88%91%E5%B0%8D%E4%BA%8B%E6%88%91%E5%B0%8D%E4%BA%BA%E6%88%91%E5%B0%8D%E6%88%91/</link> <pubDate>Fri, 12 Dec 2025 08:29:23 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://wenchiehlee.github.io/mkdocs-life/feed_rss_updated.xml">Wen-Chieh Lee的生活</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://wenchiehlee.github.io/mkdocs-life/blog/2025/12/%E8%B2%AA%E5%97%94%E7%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%BA%95%E5%B1%A4%E9%82%8F%E8%BC%AF%E6%88%91%E5%B0%8D%E4%BA%8B%E6%88%91%E5%B0%8D%E4%BA%BA%E6%88%91%E5%B0%8D%E6%88%91/</guid> </item> </channel></rss>